title: Best of The Program | Guests: Megyn Kelly & Sharyl Attkisson | 5/12/20
description:
Elon Musk is reopening his California Tesla plant, even if it means jail. Investigative reporter Sharyl Attkisson joins with her new definitive list of media mistakes in the Trump era and why she believes Flynn was targeted by the FBI: He knew where the “bodies” were buried. Journalist Megyn Kelly dives into her groundbreaking Tara Reade interview and how dishonest the media has become.
